= Fetch PointInstancer Points =
#context: sop
#type: node

"""Fetches point data from a USD PointInstancer primitive into SOP geometry."""

== Overview ==

Fetch PointInstancer Points reads the instance positions, orientations, scales, and prototype indices from a USD PointInstancer primitive and outputs them as SOP point geometry. This allows PointInstancer data to be processed or visualized at the SOP level.

@parameters

LOP Path:
    #id: lop_path
    Path to the LOP node whose stage contains the PointInstancer primitive.

Primitive:
    #id: primitive
    USD path to the PointInstancer primitive to fetch.
